<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer__inner container">

    <div class="footer__brand">
      <a href="/" class="footer__logo">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2C8 7 4 10 4 14a8 8 0 0 0 16 0c0-4-4-7-8-12z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        <span>HEATFORGE</span>
      </a>
      <p class="footer__tagline">Кузница огня с 2019 года.<br>Ручная работа — каждый шов, каждый угол.</p>

      <div class="footer__payments">
        <p class="footer__payments-label">Принимаем оплату</p>
        <div class="footer__payments-list">
          <span class="payment-badge payment-badge--mir">МИР</span>
          <span class="payment-badge payment-badge--sber">SberPay</span>
          <span class="payment-badge payment-badge--tpay">T-Pay</span>
          <span class="payment-badge payment-badge--visa">VISA</span>
          <span class="payment-badge payment-badge--mc">MC</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer__delivery">
        <p class="footer__delivery-label">Доставка</p>
        <div class="footer__delivery-list">
          <span class="delivery-badge">СДЭК</span>
          <span class="delivery-badge">ПЭК</span>
          <span class="delivery-badge">Почта РФ</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="footer__nav" aria-label="Каталог">
      <h4 class="footer__nav-title">Каталог</h4>
      <ul class="footer__nav-list">
        <li><a href="/catalog?category=grill">Грили и мангалы</a></li>
        <li><a href="/catalog?category=accessory">Аксессуары</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog">Рецепты</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <nav class="footer__nav" aria-label="Информация">
      <h4 class="footer__nav-title">Информация</h4>
      <ul class="footer__nav-list">
        <li><a href="/about">О компании</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contacts">Доставка и оплата</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contacts">Гарантия</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog">Блог</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contacts">Контакты</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="footer__contact">
      <h4 class="footer__nav-title">Есть вопрос?</h4>
      <p>Напишите нам в WhatsApp — ответим за 10 минут.</p>
      <a href="{{ app.whatsapp }}" class="btn btn--whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        Написать в WhatsApp
      </a>
      <p class="footer__phone">или <a href="tel:{{ app.phone }}">{{ app.phone }}</a></p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="footer__bottom">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; {{ app.year }} HeatForge. Все права защищены.</p>
      <div class="footer__bottom-links">
        <a href="/privacy">Политика конфиденциальности</a>
        <a href="/offer">Публичная оферта</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
